    "(95) explored AI's transformative impact on the dental industry, focusing on its potential to enhance diagnostic and treatment accuracy.",
    "The study addresses AI's application in various dental care aspects, including sophisticated imaging, disease detection, and the creation of personalized treatment plans.",
    "It also considers ethical and privacy concerns related to AI in dentistry, envisioning a future where AI-integrated dental practices lead to more efficient, patient-centered, and effective oral health outcomes, emphasizing the shift towards leveraging technology to improve the quality of patient care.",
    "According to Cheng et al.",
    "(96) and Hassam et al."
